
// Lab Execution Steps //

1. Open a terminal prompt and execute below command to copy the project files into the Spark docker container.

	# docker cp /home/labuser/Project hdp_spark-master:/

2. Login to Spark container and launch a Spark-shell for executing the scala code.

	# docker exec -i -t hdp_spark-master bash
	# ./spark/bin/spark-shell

3. Open the FitnessTrackerDataJob.txt file present in the Project/Code/ location and execute the code on the Spark shell (scala).

4. Please refer Project videos for step wise execution.
 
